.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, fuchsia, blood-red
There are 3 different nationalities: german, pakistani, russian
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram
1. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the pakistani##1
6. the person driving the car is in an odd position##4
7. the person who likes coral is between the pakistani and the person driving the tram##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | coffee    | soy-milk  |
| Color         | blood-red        | coral   | fuchsia   |
| Nationality   | russian       | german    | pakistani |
| Transport     | tram          | quad-bike | car       |

