.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-4-19::.
There 3 different types of food: apricot, cranberry, lettuce
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, indie, punk
3 different games are played: domino, bridge, snooker
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, rugby
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating lettuce##1
5. the person playing snooker is in an even position##4
6. the fan of house is the person playing bridge##1
7. the person playing domino is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating cranberry is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |
| Food          | cranberry  | apricot   | lettuce |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | punk      | house   |
| Game   | domino     | snooker | bridge |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | cricket   | rugby   |

